Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.17,0:07:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}（針生）\Nよ～し　じゃあ やるか　西田
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.47,0:07:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}えっ！　まさか…
